raw_data.subTitle: 31.5M views
raw_data.description:
POP MART Super Brand Day —— Trick Treat POP! 👻✨ 
This Halloween, POP MART invites you to show your spooky creativity!
Join the #TrickTreatPOP challenge in your own style:
🕷️ Transform yourself into SKULLPANDA, CRYBABY, Hirono, or other POP MART characters with Halloween makeup & cosplay.
🎃 Or, dress up your POP MART blind boxes and figures with Halloween vibes – pumpkins, cobwebs, candy magic, you name it!
📅 Challenge runs from October 13th until November 2nd.
🏆 Winners will receive exclusive POP MART prizes!
👉 Use #popmart #popmartSBD #TrickTreatPOP when posting your video on TikTok, and @popmart.uk.online – join one challenge, or both!
✨ Time to trick, treat & POP this Halloween!

T&C:
Eligibility: Open to residents aged 18+ in the UK.
Entry Period: From 00:00 on 13/10/2025 until 23:59 on 02/11/2025 (UK local time).
How to Enter: Participants post a video or image content featuring POP MART products and include the required hashtags: #POPMARTSBD #TreatThickPOP @popmart.uk.online, The content should follow the transformation challenge prompts recommended on the POP MART Online Store UK. Posting this way qualifies as an entry.
Winner Selection: Six winners will be selected from all eligible entries during the campaign period.
Prize: Each winner will receive a Surpries Series vinyl plush/blind box. Winners will be notified via email. Delivery arrangements will be completed following the notification.
Account Requirements: TikTok/Instagram accounts must be public during the campaign to validate entries.
Announcement & Contact: Winners will be contacted via DM within 7 days after the campaign ends.
General: POP MART reserves the right of final interpretation of this campaign and its rules. Full terms and conditions apply.
